HEADWORD: Imperturbation
<hw>Im*per`tur*ba"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>imperturbatio</ets>.]</ety> <def>Freedom from agitation of mind;
calmness; quietude.</def> <rj><au>W. Montagu.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
